      <data key="d0">ONE RS 1-Inch 360 Edition</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">ONE RS 1-Inch 360 Edition is a discontinued Insta360 camera model that requires specific USB mode settings for SDK control.&lt;SEP&gt;The ONE RS 1-Inch 360 Edition is a discontinued 360 camera model from Insta360.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3b8756d733f712e9cc58b5b2ce82c5f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c02cbfca3d759f3fc74441722e33b7f</data>
