    <node id="X3">
      <data key="d0">X3</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">The X3 is a current 360 camera model from Insta360.&lt;SEP&gt;X3 is an Insta360 camera model that requires USB mode settings for SDK control.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3b8756d733f712e9cc58b5b2ce82c5f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c02cbfca3d759f3fc74441722e33b7f</data>
      <data key="d4">README.md</data>
