    <node id="X4">
      <data key="d0">X4</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">The X4 is a camera model mentioned in the text, with specific requirements for shooting modes and preview stream resolution.&lt;SEP&gt;X4 is an Insta360 camera model that requires USB mode settings for SDK control.&lt;SEP&gt;The X4 is a current 360 camera model from Insta360.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3b8756d733f712e9cc58b5b2ce82c5f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a52890f02528b7a7e6ee6cdbd3a1ee16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c02cbfca3d759f3fc74441722e33b7f</data>
