      <data key="d0">camera._connect</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">The 'camera._connect' event involves synchronizing time between the client and the camera, and returns detailed camera information upon successful connection.&lt;SEP&gt;camera._connect is a command in the Insta360 Pro Camera API used to establish a connection with the camera.&lt;SEP&gt;camera._connect is a command used to establish a connection with a camera, requiring parameters like hardware time and time zone.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-4ebfc5a85834e7af502df36580b269e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d473841de4b15fa50236282c202acd6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30f55c23379fa246af6d173ec3cc8323</data>
