    <node id="Built-in Http Server">
      <data key="d0">Built-in Http Server</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The built-in HTTP server in Insta360 Pro series cameras facilitates communication via the API, supporting commands, state polling, and file access.</data>
